Sayang.

26
00:02:01,370 --> 00:02:02,400
Kak Hyeon Woo!

27
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,599
Apa kabar?

28
00:02:11,009 --> 00:02:13,310
Ayah, ini kakak yang kubicarakan.

29
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,810
Dia ayahku.

30
00:02:19,349 --> 00:02:20,449
Halo.

31
